{"tid":400163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"包皮係咪一定要割?","createTime":"2017-09-14T14:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T15:03:58.000Z","uid":119105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c9d946effe9ca8adf75e743c5d704e25331aab3","tid":400163,"uid":119105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:31:17.000Z","msg":"唔割包係咪扑唔到野?"},{"pid":"ac1331d63640fba6836f63f990bd992dbe6c55e2","tid":400163,"uid":83906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:33:06.000Z","msg":"一定要"},{"pid":"bbb40e7825d6af281fbff6edb319510a44507eb3","tid":400163,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:33:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ae78a35d35a03271d6771c97fa4e76d6c1049b9","tid":400163,"uid":9286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:45:31.000Z","msg":"睇你包皮過長嚴唔嚴重<br />\n每日沖涼用手反少少<br />\n如果最後好努力都反唔到先要割<br />\n<br />\n細個比醫生check 幾次都反唔到<br />\n有日沖沖下涼自己好奇去反<br />\n開頭有少少痛 跟住出多少少力就反到"},{"pid":"39eb3787dad57dc2363731f982d83880f1f3e746","tid":400163,"uid":79081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"有無人係平時反到,扯緊果陣完全反唔到"},{"pid":"f1962ead602c996665db8fec0e36e7ba1e4d7cea","tid":400163,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"留名，<br />\n唔扯反到<br />\n扯左反會有啲痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bd6e8f6e6eb1cf87f5a9c1f8649381ee0a6401","tid":400163,"uid":113921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:53:04.000Z","msg":"一定要割。<br />\n唔割既話，會影響將來性生活。<br />\n愈早割，愈冇咁痛。<br />\n所謂：早割早享受，遲割買難受。"},{"pid":"5bffbb1327eea94726999d729d141f45e14b57a4","tid":400163,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人係平時反到,扯緊果陣完全反唔到</blockquote><br />\n一扯變硬 龜頭變大 塊皮已經包佢唔住自動反左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為平時